# Project intelligence (Cursor)

- Prefer **absolute paths** in tool calls when possible.
- This repo is a **static site** using Jekyll for GitHub Pages deployment.
- Main pages (`index.html`, `project.html`) use `layout: null` — they are self-contained HTML.
- Legacy pages (`about.html`) redirect to `/` via meta-refresh.
- CSS lives in `assets/css/style.css` — dark futuristic theme with CSS variables.
- JS lives in `assets/js/main.js` — custom cursor, typewriter, counters, scroll reveal, canvas particles, project filters.
- Fonts: Syne (display), Inter (body), JetBrains Mono (code) — loaded via Google Fonts.
- Color scheme: `#06060b` background, `#00d4ff` accent, `#7b61ff` secondary accent.
- Images: `assets/images/logo.png` (brand), `assets/images/pedro-profile.png` (profile photo).
- Projects are hardcoded in `project.html` (not using `_data/projects.json` anymore).
- Blog still uses Jekyll layouts (`_layouts/post.html`).
